www.OSRG.net/sheepdog >>Sheepdog is a distributed storage system for KVM. It provides highly available block level storage volumes that can be attached to KVM virtual machines. Sheepdog scales to several hundreds nodes, and supports advanced volume management features such as snapshot, cloning, and thin provisioning.

Omemo.com >>Omemo is an open source social storage platform. Store your files online, share your stuff and browse what other users store in the world's largest multimedia library: The Omemo peer-to-peer virtual hard-drive. 

